    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The expected outcomes of this project include: (1) equitable and increased access for girls, adolescent girls and women, including those with disabilities, to inclusive and quality education and learning opportunities; and (2) equitable and coordinated provision of safe, quality and gender-sensitive formal and non-formal education for girls, adolescent girls and boys and women.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Les r&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s de ce projet comprennent : 1) acc&#xE8;s &#xE9;quitable et accru des filles, des adolescentes et des femmes, y compris celles en situation de handicap, &#xE0; l&#x2019;&#xE9;ducation et aux opportunit&#xE9;s d&#x2019;apprentissage inclusives et de qualit&#xE9;; 2) prestation &#xE9;quitable et coordonn&#xE9;e d&#x2019;une &#xE9;ducation formelle et non-formelle s&#xE9;curitaire, de qualit&#xE9; et sensible au genre en faveur des filles, des adolescent(e)s et des femmes.</narrative>
